snippet.title: Minecraft Legends - Nintendo Direct Mini: Partner Showcase | 6.28.2022
snippet.description:
Minecraft Legends is coming to Nintendo Switch in 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/minecraft-legends-switch/

Discover the mysteries of Minecraft Legends, a new action strategy game. Lead your allies in heroic battles to defend the Overworld from the destructive piglins.

#MinecraftLegends #NintendoSwitch
